---
// TicketHeader.astro
---
<header class="bg-ticket-accent text-white p-8 pb-10 relative">
  <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight leading-none">Pollada<br/>Solidaria</h1>
    <span class="font-mono text-sm opacity-80 border border-white/30 px-2 py-1 rounded">Nº 001</span>
  </div>
  <p class="text-white/90 text-sm font-medium mb-2 leading-relaxed">
    Acompáñanos en esta actividad pro-salud. Tu colaboración nos ayuda a cubrir gastos médicos urgentes.
  </p>
  <div class="font-mono text-xs opacity-75 mt-4">
    <p>FECHA: Sábado 24 de Agosto</p>
    <p>HORA: 12:00 PM - 5:00 PM</p>
    <p>PRECIO: S/ 15.00 x Porción</p>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Cutout circles for ticket effect -->
  <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-3 w-6 h-6 bg-ticket-bg rounded-full"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-6 h-6 bg-ticket-bg rounded-full"></div>
</header>
